data.description: Excellent location! This home is spacious and has so much potential! The lot is huge, views are beautiful and so close to the hospital.A bit dated in decor but can easily be renovated with just paint and cabinets, appliances. There are bonus rooms, 16x20 sunroom, storage rooms and additions Built in approximately 1965, the Foundation has 7.5 walls all open with a hidden bomb shelter. Two bay garage with a large side storage room you wouldn't know was there! Schedule a viewing, seeing is believing!
